</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_line_1576485889988_3893">cʒeitlich vor
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kundt</expan> werde / . vnd ob vns die
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> kere ıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_line_1576485902169_3908">
<expan>hind<ex>er</ex>n</expan> würd <del rend="strikethrough">daʒ man </del>
